high_descs: Begin walking across the room, then hang a left and walk over to the small silver bin on the ground next to the counter.
Pick up the wine bottle out of the silver bin.
Turn left and begin walking across the room, then hang a right and walk over to the black fridge.
Open the fridge and put the wine bottle inside then close the door, after a couple seconds open the fridge and remove the wine bottle then close the fridge door again.
Turn right and begin walking across the room, turn left at the end of the counter to face the toaster.
Put the chilled wine bottle on the front edge of the counter two tiles to the left of the spatula.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled wine bottle on the counter.

high_descs: Go left and walk to the end of the counter and turn left again to face the trash can.
Pick the bottle up out of the trash can.
Go left and the right to stand in front of the fridge.
Put the bottle in the fridge, shut the door and then open the door and pick the bottle up, shut the door again.
Go right and stop at the far end of the counter in front of the toaster.
Put the bottle on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled bottle on the counter.

high_descs: Turn left to go straight across the room. Then turn around to find the trash can.
Pick up the glass bottle from the trash can.
Take the bottle and go right around the counter to the fridge, on the right.
Place the bottle inside the fridge and shut the door. Take the bottle out and shut the door again.
Carry the bottle to the right, down to the other side of the counter where the toaster is.
Place the bottle on the counter in front of the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Chill a bottle and place it on the counter.
